  "detailed_description": "<h1>Use of controllers is highly recommended for this product</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/851d3560df572e1465eb1fed039caf32.webp?t=1562665020\" width=46 height=46 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/0312498b8537a96e118fdd370614829b.webp?t=1562665020\" width=46 height=46 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/9cfeee8fdc6517ab059fbacc11c7af45.webp?t=1562665020\" width=46 height=46 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/7a5e97f048f59f7fdf4be76525dd3089.webp?t=1562665020\" width=46 height=46 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/c0d8f4153ad574d2e3facd77838652b2.webp?t=1562665020\" width=46 height=46 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/2768de86a48d75fffb8396592efa7634.webp?t=1562665020\" width=399 height=60 /></span><br>It's golden age of piracy and somewhere on the high seas there is a legendary bay where all manner of rowdy scallywags gather to wage battle on very important pirate games: for who wins is the king of pirates and who loses is the salty seabird!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/ab819fdc35ede833e0ddc71652d34c23.poster.avif?t=1562665020\" width=588 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/ab819fdc35ede833e0ddc71652d34c23.webm?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/ab819fdc35ede833e0ddc71652d34c23.mp4?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/f9c793366a7e3af03323dbb3b65f57a3.webp?t=1562665020\" width=399 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Four unique game modes<br></li><li>Race mode (championship)<br></li><li>Mermaids<br></li><li>Eight notorious pirate captains to choose from<br></li><li>Sharks<br></li><li>Multiple settings for each game mode: Modes inside game modes<br></li><li>Treasure hunting<br></li><li>Swashbuckling original soundtrack<br></li><li>Hours of crazy fun local multi-player action... It's good 'ol fun!<br></li><li>Pirate cards<br></li><li>The Kraken<br></li><li>Naval warfare action<br></li><li>Drunken Sailor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/5998699a2a95ed9cb773b72edb307ad6.poster.avif?t=1562665020\" width=588 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/5998699a2a95ed9cb773b72edb307ad6.webm?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/5998699a2a95ed9cb773b72edb307ad6.mp4?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game modes in Salty Seabird Bay are are easy to learn, but have depth to be to be played for long time.<br><br>No landlubbers allowed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/1cbadd138cd068784b2a09b430d17758.poster.avif?t=1562665020\" width=588 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/1cbadd138cd068784b2a09b430d17758.webm?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/868180/extras/1cbadd138cd068784b2a09b430d17758.mp4?t=1562665020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Salty Seabird Bay is the ultimate local multi-player pirate party game bonanza! </strong>",
